OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'There is no right or wrong
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fway to have alopecia'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Gail Porter has been praised by        
OL,6, campaigners and people living with     
OL,7, alopecia after she posed for a         
OL,8, photoshoot with a wig for the first    
OL,9, time this week.                        
OL,11,FIn a photoshoot for the Sun, the       
OL,12,FScottish TV presenter said she loves   
OL,13,Fbeing bald - but her new wig will give 
OL,14,Fher an opportunity to do different     
OL,15,Fthings.                                
OL,17,FFor many people who have alopecia like 
OL,18,FGail, choosing whether to wear a wig   
OL,19,Fand other accessories can be a tough   
OL,20,Fcall to make.                          
